      .medium-8.columns
        ol
          li We recommend the Chrome web browser
          li Web meetings use the microphone and your camera on your computer
          li Coordinate the meeting time with your team members
          li Visit your company or alliance listing and click the web meeting link
          li Take advantage of the chat and screen sharing features

